                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. DOANE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Plenty of other persons have them? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes—I swear to these—it is not possible for me to miss any—we have 200 bags in at a time.</p>
